  namespace Kestrel
    /-!
      A bird `K` is a *kestrel* if for any birds `x` and `y`,
      the result of applying `K` to `x` and then applying the result to `y`
      is `x`.

      This is similar to the mathematical concept of a "projection" or "idempotent".

      https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kestrel
    -/

    -- the definition of a kestrel
    axiom K : Bird
    axiom K.call : ∀ (x y : Bird), (K ◁ x) ◁ y = x

